<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12070d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12070d">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12070d"> 70(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> du dernier bien</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Le menu est de choix, puisque c&apos;est la f&ecirc;te &laquo;du patron Saint Maur&raquo;; M. de la Chasti&egrave;re se retire enchant&eacute;, mais voici qu&apos;une heure apr&egrave;s, le couvent est envahi par les soldats de la garde. Mme de la Chasti&egrave;re, furieuse sans doute de n&apos;avoir pas &eacute;t&eacute; invit&eacute;e avec son mari, a donn&eacute; l&apos;ordre &agrave; certains officiers avec lesquels elle est probablement &laquo;<mark>du dernier bien</mark>&raquo;, de faire envahir le monast&egrave;re; mais les religieux r&eacute;sistent et il faut chasser de haute lutte les trois fr&egrave;res portiers, auxquels les sbires du gouverneur finissent par &laquo;ravir les clefs du chasteau&raquo;. <br><font color="green">[There is a choice menu because it is the feast of &ldquo;the patron Saint Maur&rdquo;; M. de la Chasti&egrave;re retires overjoyed, but not an hour later the convent is invaded by soldiers of the guard. Mme de la Chasti&egrave;re, no doubt furious that she has not been invited with her husband, has ordered a number of officers with whom she is probably &ldquo;close,&rdquo; to invade the monastery; but the religious resist and a big fight is necessary to get rid of the three brother-gatekeepers, from whom the governor&apos;s henchmen &ldquo;ravish the keys of the castle.&rdquo;]</font> <small> &Eacute;tienne Dupont, <a name="SMIN" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#SMIN"><cite title="source">Le Mont Saint-Michel Inconnu</cite></a> (1912) 308</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: Fr. <i>Du dernier bien</i>: literally &lsquo;of the last good&rsquo;, meaning &lsquo;as well as it is possible to be&rsquo;. One says euphemistically that a man is <i>du dernier bien</i> with a woman to express the fact that he is her lover. </mm> </dd></dl>
